---
const videoId = "yzvjGA1sIB4";
const embedUrl = `https://www.youtube.com/embed/${videoId}`;
---

<section
  id="trainer"
  class="relative bg-brand-primary text-brand-bg"
  aria-labelledby="trainer-heading"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-28 sm:px-10 sm:py-36 lg:px-16 lg:py-44">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-y-14 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-x-16">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <p class="caption text-brand-accent">The Trainer</p>
        <h2
          id="trainer-heading"
          class="mt-6 text-balance font-serif text-4xl leading-[1.05] sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
        >
          Meet <em class="not-italic font-serif italic text-brand-accent">Matt.</em>
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-8 max-w-md space-y-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-bg/75 sm:text-xl">
          <p>
            I started Campbell K9's because I kept meeting dogs who were being
            under-asked and over-managed. The good ones — the ones families
            really want — need structure, yes, but they also need trust,
            movement, and a sense of humor.
          </p>
          <p>
            We train seriously, but we don’t take ourselves too seriously. Most
            days that means muddy boots, a balanced pack, and a dog who finally
            understands what’s expected of him.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="caption mt-10 text-brand-bg/55">
          &mdash; Matt Campbell, Lead Trainer
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-7">
        <div
          class="relative mx-auto max-w-[360px] overflow-hidden border border-brand-bg/15 shadow-2xl"
          style="aspect-ratio: 9 / 16;"
        >
          <iframe
            src={embedUrl}
            title="Meet Matt Campbell"
            class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <p class="caption mt-4 text-center text-brand-bg/45">
          Watch the intro
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
